00:20:52,678 --> 00:20:53,560
[SPEAKER_04]: Rebecca Long-Bailey.

211
00:20:54,130 --> 00:21:08,600
[SPEAKER_05]: Well I think we need to look at the reasons as to why we've set up such a radical and transformative manifesto and what I'd say in a nutshell is that our plans deliver a more regionally equal, healthier, better educated, higher investment, higher productivity economy.

