633
00:49:15,856 --> 00:49:18,803
[SPEAKER_05]: We've seen a lot of dishonesty, if I'm honest, in this campaign.

634
00:49:19,485 --> 00:49:22,712
[SPEAKER_05]: And we need to bring honesty back to politics, because it undermines trust.

635
