693
00:53:54,750 --> 00:53:59,460
[SPEAKER_06]: And making sure we take the fossil fuels out of our electricity generation.

694
00:53:59,440 --> 00:54:02,686
[SPEAKER_06]: renewables, we should be so much more ambitious.

695
00:54:02,746 --> 00:54:05,391
[SPEAKER_06]: The cost has already come down significantly.

696
00:54:05,692 --> 00:54:12,184
[SPEAKER_06]: Offshore wind is the cheapest electricity that you can now create, thanks to Liberal Democrats supporting that technology.

697
00:54:12,264 --> 00:54:20,279
[SPEAKER_04]: Let me ask you what I asked Caroline Lucas, which is your manifesto, like the Green manifesto, has talked about penalising people who fly a lot.

698
00:54:20,299 --> 00:54:22,343
