856
01:04:19,264 --> 01:04:29,920
[SPEAKER_11]: The fact is that in those documents, if the British government had wanted to, it could have explicitly said the NHS is not up for negotiations, just like the US did on issues around climate change.

857
01:04:30,160 --> 01:04:31,562
[SPEAKER_11]: It chose not to do so.

858
01:04:31,622 --> 01:04:35,428
[SPEAKER_11]: So we are absolutely right to say that the NHS is at risk here.

859
01:04:35,408 --> 01:04:36,811
