[SPEAKER_04]: Hello.

935
01:10:47,341 --> 01:10:48,061
[SPEAKER_04]: Please, your question.

936
01:10:48,502 --> 01:10:48,602
Yeah.

937
01:10:48,802 --> 01:10:54,533
[SPEAKER_00]: UK immigration laws don't treat EU and non-EU citizens equally now.

938
01:10:55,394 --> 01:10:58,781
[SPEAKER_00]: Should this change, no matter whether we leave or remain?

939
01:10:59,742 --> 01:11:05,834
