953
01:12:11,823 --> 01:12:13,967
[SPEAKER_11]: And I'm very proud to stand up for freedom of movement.

954
01:12:14,007 --> 01:12:20,016
[SPEAKER_11]: I think it's been an extraordinary gift to this country to be able to travel and study and live and love in 27 other countries.

955
01:12:20,036 --> 01:12:25,004
[SPEAKER_11]: I think it's been an extraordinary gift for people from our country to go there and for them to come here.

956
01:12:25,044 --> 01:12:30,593
[SPEAKER_11]: So I'm proud to stand up on this platform and to say that I believe in the power of freedom of movement.

957
01:12:30,613 --> 01:12:31,814
[SPEAKER_11]: And I think it's a positive thing.

958
01:12:32,035 --> 01:12:32,856
[SPEAKER_11]: What I also think

