[SPEAKER_04]: People in the EU get freedom of movement, people in the rest of the world do not.

961
01:12:38,283 --> 01:12:51,942
[SPEAKER_11]: I would like to see a levelling upwards when it comes to fairness, because what I'm deeply worried about is the kinds of rules, for example, that will break up families, that will end up in things like immigration detention, that has things like a minimum income rule.

962
01:12:52,242 --> 01:12:53,944
[SPEAKER_11]: I think all of those are deeply unfair.

963
01:12:54,045 --> 01:12:57,409
[SPEAKER_11]: Family reunion ought to be supported, so we need fair immigration rules.

964
01:12:57,389 --> 01:13:01,579
