[SPEAKER_05]: We want every single EU citizen who's here in the UK to remain with full rights and protections, and we want that reciprocated for UK nationals in the EU.

990
01:15:17,311 --> 01:15:27,622
[SPEAKER_05]: Now, on the wider system of immigration and what that could look like, obviously that would be part of negotiations, but it has to be sensible and it has to be fair and it has to work for businesses and the economy.

991
01:15:27,922 --> 01:15:34,549
[SPEAKER_05]: We've got over 43,000 vacancies in the NHS for nurses, for example, and we need to fill them immediately while we train up

992
01:15:34,529 --> 01:15:37,792
[SPEAKER_05]: our own nurses to be able to carry out those roles in the future.

993
01:15:37,812 --> 01:15:39,694
[SPEAKER_05]: We've got to be sensible about this.

994
